txml

Interface StartElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    XMLEvent, XMLStreamConstants
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TStartElement

    public interface StartElement
extends XMLEvent
    The StartElement interface provides access to information about start elements. A StartElement is reported for each Start Tag in the document.
    Author:
    Tomas Kunovsky

    • Method Detail

      • getNamespaces

        Iterator getNamespaces()
        Returns an Iterator of namespaces declared on this element. This Iterator does not contain previously declared namespaces unless they appear on the current START_ELEMENT. Therefore this list may contain redeclared namespaces and duplicate namespace declarations. Returns an empty iterator if there are no namespaces.
        Returns:
        a readonly Iterator over Namespace interfaces, or an empty iterator
